n%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20crying%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20arrest%20memo%C2%A0mentioned%20pre-existing%20'injury%20marks%20under%20her%20eyes'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Rao's%20counsel%20also%20claimed%20the%2033-year-old%20had%20not%20been%20made%20aware%20of%20her%20rights%20when%20she%20was%20arrested%2C%20and%20that%20there%20were%20multiple%20protocol%20violations%20when%20a%20team%20from%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%2C%20or%20DRI%2C%20took%20her%20into%20custody%20as%20she%20was%20leaving%20the%20Bengaluru%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%2C%20for%20example%2C%20she%20gave%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20voluntary%26quot%3B%2C%20her%20lawyer%20said%2C%20urging%20the%20court%20to%20therefore%20rule%20it%20inadmissible.%20It%20was%20also%20argued%20an%20'arrest%20declaration'%20by%20the%20DRI%20is%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20finally%2C%20Ms%20Rao%20claimed%20a%20violation%20of%20Section%20102%20of%20the%20Customs%20Act%2C%20which%20says%20an%20arrested%20suspect%20must%20be%20immediately%20produced%20before%20a%20magistrate%20if%20s%2Fhe%20requests%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20it%20was%20pointed%20out%2C%20was%20part%20of%20guidelines%20set%20out%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20noted%20%26quot%3Bcourts%20have%20been%20granting%20bail%20in%20murder%20cases%20if%20accused%20is%20a%20lady%26quot%3B.%20Her%20lawyer%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20cannot%20she%20be%20granted%20bail%20for%20this%2C%20where%20the%20quantum%20of%20punishment%20is%20less%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stepdaughter%20of%20Ramachandra%20Rao%20-%20a%20senior%20police%20official%20serving%20as%20Chairman%20and%20Managing%20Director%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20State%20Police%20Housing%20Corporation%20-%20Ms%20Rao%20was%20caught%20on%20March%203%20after%20she%20arrived%20from%20Dubai%20with%20gold%20bars%20worth%20Rs%2014.56%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20searched%20her%20hou