20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanalysis-owlet-baby-care-spac-deal-presentation-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOwlet%20Dream%20Sock%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(an%20app-linked%20%26quot%3Bsmart%20sock%26quot%3B%20that%20lets%20parents%20track%20their%20baby's%20vital%20metrics)%20and%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fparenting%2Fnanit-plus-smart-baby-monitor-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENanit%20Plus%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20smart%20baby%20monitor%20(whose%20night-vision-equipped%20video%20camera%20can%20track%20an%20infant's%20breathing)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20slew%20of%20WiFi-enabled%20breast%20pumps%20(including%20a%20nearly%20%24400%20model%20from%20Elvie).%20Between%202018%20and%202019%2C%20submissions%20to%20CES's%20Best%20of%20Baby%20Tech%20Awards%20increased%20by%2088%25.%20And%20in%202024%2C%20EMARKETER%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcontent-na1.emarketer.com%2Fus-retail-industry-ad-spending-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efound%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20products%20for%20babies%20and%20children%20had%20the%20fastest-growing%20digital%20ad%20spend%20of%20any%20market%20category.%20These%20days%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20avoid%20the%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20moms%20who%20have%20taken%20to%20TikTok%20to%20show%20off%20their%20favorite%20devices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20more%20millennial%20and%20Gen%20Z%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20natives%26quot%3B%20become%20parents%2C%20it's%20no%20surprise%20that%20devices%20providing%20real-time%20data%20on%20a%20baby's%20squirms%2C%20temperature%20shifts%2C%20and%20even%20bowel%20movements%20are%20hot%20commodities.%20But%20while%20this%20information%20is%20reassuring%20to%20some%20parents%2C%20it%20can%20exacerbate%20anxiety%20in%20others%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20those%20already%20struggling%20during%20the%20fraught%2C%20sleep-deprived%20months%20of%20early%20parenthood.%20Instead%20of%20fueling%20connection%2C%20some%20of%20the%20products%20might%20even%20make%20parents%20less%20attuned%20to%20their%20kids%20and%20to%20themselves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20the%20baby-tech%20industry%20has%20been%20sown%20in%20the%20threat%20of%20worst-case%20scenarios.%20The%20first%20commercial%20baby%20monitor%20%E2%80%94%20a%20simple%20radio-based%20device%20%E2%80%94%20landed%20in%20American%20nurseries%20in%201938%2C%20a%20mere%20six%20years%20after%20the%20nation%20was%20rocked%20by%20the%20kidnapping%20and%20murder%20of%20the%20aviator%20Charles%20Lindbergh's%2020-month-old%20son.%20In%20the%201980s%20and%20'90s%2C%20the%20devices%20became%20commonplace%20as%20fear%20spread%20about%20cases%20of%20sudden%20infant%20death%20syndrome%20in%20babies'%20cribs.%20By%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-doesnt-use-baby-monitor-no-anxiety-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebaby%20monitors%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20were%20getting%20regular%20tech%20upgrades%2C%20from%20cameras%20and%20two-way%20communication%20to%20heart-rate%20and%20temperature%20monitoring%20and%20even%20REM%20sleep%20cycle%20detection.%20Though%20these%20updates%20weren't%20necessarily%20filling%20a%20void%20in%20what%20parents%20needed%2C%20they%20quickly%20found%20a%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecca%20Susong%2C%20a%20Chattanooga%2C%20Tennessee%2C%20pediatrician%20and%20perinatal%20care%20consultant%2C%20says%20fear%20of%20SIDS%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20major%20driver%20behind%20parents'%20interest%20in%20purchasing%20the%20WiFi-connected%2C%20app-paired%20baby%20monitors%20that%20emerged%20after%20the%20rise%20of%20smartphones.%20Some%20parents%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20those%20with%20neonatal%20intensive%20care%20unit%20experiences%20or%20past%20health%20scares%20%E2%80%94%20say%20they%20feel%20reassured%20by%20features%20like%20oxygen%20and%20heart-rate%20tracking.%20But%20there's%20no%20clear%20evidence%20linking%20baby%20monitors%20to%20a%20decrease%20in%20cases%20of%20SIDS%2C%20so%20the%20American%20Academy%20of%20Pediatrics%20actually%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublications.aap.org%2Fpediatrics%2Farticle%2F150%2F1%2Fe2022057990%2F188304%2FSleep-Related-Infant-Deaths-Updated-2022%3Fautologincheck%3Dredirected%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecautions%20against%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20monitoring%20for%20it%20at%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20tend%20not%20to%20recommend%20getting%20the%20high-tech%20kind%2C%26quot%3B%20Susong%20says%20about%20baby%20monitors%2C%20citing%20their%20high%20costs%20and%20unnecessary%20bells%20and%20whistles.%20Instead%2C%20she%20redirects%20the%20discussion%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprevent-baby-death-new-advice-sleep-alone-flat-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esleep%20safety%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20like%20using%20a%20firm%20mattress%20with%20nothing%20else%20in%20the%20crib%20and%20putting%20the%20baby%20on%20their%20back%20to%20sleep%20%E2%80%94%20tangible%2C%20science-backed%20methods%20for%20averting%20SIDS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20they%20give%20people%20a%20sense%20of%20control%20over%20something%20that%20feels%20very%20uncertain%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Emily%20Guarnotta%2C%20a%20Long%20Island%20clinical%20psychologist%20who%20specializes%20in%20perinatal%20mental%20health.%20%26quot%3BSIDS%20is%20terrifying%20because%20it's%20so%20unpredictable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGuarnotta%20says%20she's%20observed%20that%20type%20A%2C%20control-seeking%20parents%20are%20particularly%20prone%20to%20look%20for%20reassurance%20from%20baby-monitoring%20devices.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20times%20when%20fear%20of%20something%20happening%20is%20already%20present%2C%20and%20then%20a%20product%20comes%20along%20or%20is%20recommended%2C%20and%20you%20think%2C%20'This%20is%20going%20to%20help%20me.%20This%20will%20make%20me%20feel%20better%20and%20keep%20my%20baby%20safe%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt%20can%20turn%20into%20a%20vicious%20cycle%20%E2%80%94%20you%20get%20some%20relief%20from%20using%20the%20product%2C%20but%20then%20the%20anxiety%20returns%2C%20and%20the%20cycle%20repeats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDavid%20Lesner%2C%20a%2039-year-old%20software%20engineer%20who%20lives%20in%20Israel%2C%20acknowledges%20that%20part%20of%20the%20initial%20appeal%20of%20a%20smart%20baby%20monitor%20was%20the%20gadgetry%20itself.%20Before%20his%2011-month-old%20son%20was%20born%2C%20he%20spent%20countless%20hours%20descending%20into%20Reddit%20rabbit%20holes%20to%20figure%20out%20which%20models%20parents%20liked%20best.%20But%20Lesner%20says%20that%20even%20his%20final%2C%20meticulously%20considered%20pick%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Nanit%20Pro%20%E2%80%94%20is%20less%20than%20perfectly%20accurate.%20While%20he's%20never%20experienced%20one%20of%20the%20monitor's%20false%20alarms%20that%20his%20baby%20had%20stopped%20breathing%20or%20moving%2C%20he%20says%20he%20knows%20others%20who%20have.%20%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20very%20terrifying%2C%26quot%3B%20Lesner%20says.%20%26quot%3BThose%20three%20seconds%20that%20you%20are%20going%20from%20one%20room%20to%20another%20to%20see%20that%20your%20child%20is%20fine%20can%20be%20like%20an%20eternity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20even%20a%20few%20false%20alarms%20could%20deter%20Logan%20Blackburn-Issitt%2C%20a%2041-year-old%20entrepreneur%20in%20the%20West%20Midlands%2C%20England%2C%20who%20used%20infant-movement-detection%20devices%20with%20all%20six%20of%20his%20children.%20The%20four%20older%20kids%2C%20now%20between%207%20and%2013%2C%20slept%20on%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fraise-your-kids-entirely-online-2013-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAngelcare%20sensor%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20pad%2C%20which%20sounds%20an%20alarm%20if%20it%20doesn't%20detect%20movement%20for%2020%20seconds.%20The%20youngest%2C%203-year-old%20twins%2C%20wore%20Snuza%20Hero%20movement%20monitors%20clipped%20onto%20their%20diapers.%20If%20Blackburn-Issitt%20or%20his%20partner%20forgot%20to%20switch%20off%20the%20pad%20when%20they%20lifted%20their%20babies%20out%20of%20the%20crib%2C%20or%20if%20the%20Snuzas%20got%20jostled%20out%20of%20place%2C%20the%20devices%20would%20blare.%20But%20if%20anything%2C%20these%20occasional%20mishaps%20only%20fortified%20his%20peace%20of%20mind.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20babies%20stopped%20breathing%2C%20we%20would%20be%20alerted%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEventually%2C%20baby-tech%20merchants%20got%20a%20little%20carried%20away%20by%20the%20market%20possibilities.%20A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-self-driving-baby-stroller-costs-brake-motors-ella-ai2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%243%2C000%20self-driving%20AI%20stroller%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%20Yours%20for%20the%20taking%2C%20courtesy%20of%20the%20Canadian%20startup%20Gl%C3%BCxkind%2C%20which%20launched%20its%20first%20of%20two%20smart-stroller%20systems%20in%202023.%20(But%20be%20warned%3A%20There's%20a%20waitlist%20for%20its%20anchor%20product%2C%20the%20Ella.)%20How%20about%20a%20Bluetooth-connected%20diaper%20sensor%20that%20spares%20caretakers%20from%20sniff-checking%20for%20number%20twos%3F%20Look%20no%20further%20than%20the%20Korean%20startup%20Monit%2C%20whose%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fmonit-to-feature-smart-baby-monitor-at-ces-2019-1027831491%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esmart-baby-monitor%20system%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20the%20talk%20of%20the%202019%20BabyTech%20Summit%20%E2%80%94%20though%20the%20high-tech%20poo%20detector%20proved%20a%20little%20too%20weird%20to%20gain%20market%20traction.%20Or%20what%20about%20an%20AI-powered%20changing%20pad%3F%20The%20startup%20Woddle%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20bring%20fresh%20data%20insights%20to%20the%20changing%20table.%20But%20it's%20still%20to%20be%20determined%20whether%20there's%20a%20real%20market%20for%20a%20tech-infused%20mat%20for%20changing%20diapers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECombining%20a%20gloss%20of%20scientific%20credibility%20with%20promises%20of%20safety%20and%20efficiency%2C%20the%20allure%20of%20baby-tech%20innovation%20outstrips%20its%20occasional%20silliness.%20The%20industry%20meets%20its%20target%20customers%20at%20the%20intersection%20of%20some%20of%20our%20most%20deeply%20entrenched%20habits.%20Millennials%2C%20who%20now%20make%20up%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-parenting-paradox-cant-afford-kids-waiting-older-career-pressure-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elargest%20share%20of%20new%20parents%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20have%20entered%20their%20child-rearing%20years%20amid%20the%20proliferation%20of%20network-connected%20home%20appliances%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffitness-tracker-step-counter-calorie-tracker-health-data-downside-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewearable%20fitness-tracking%20devices%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20urban%20infrastructure%20designed%20to%20make%20everyday%20tasks%20more%20efficient%20and%20convenient.%20In%20the%20past%20several%20years%20alone%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BInternet%20of%20Things%26quot%3B%20has%20evolved%20from%20a%20novel%20subcategory%