r-parents-snoo-doona-tripp-trapp-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESnoo%20bassinet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenting-editor-mom-of-twins-shares-her-favorite-twin-products-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDoona%20car-seat-stroller%20combo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20life-changing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20optimizing%20everything%20doesn't%20always%20make%20life%20easier.%20Ellie%20Messinger-Adams%2C%20a%20Southern%20California%20mom%20of%20two%20in%20her%20mid-30s%2C%20used%20Wyze%20baby-monitoring%20cameras%20for%20both%20of%20her%20children%2C%20now%206%20and%203%2C%20until%20about%20a%20year%20ago.%20While%20the%20cameras%20provided%20momentary%20reassurance%20that%20her%20kids%20were%20alive%20and%20well%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%2C%20checking%20them%20wound%20up%20becoming%20something%20of%20a%20compulsion.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20any%20of%20the%20cameras%20hooked%20up%20anymore%2C%20and%20it%20sort%20of%20feels%20like%20freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20mom%20is%20already%20feeling%20overwhelmed%2C%20distressed%2C%20or%20excessively%20worried%2C%20adding%20the%20responsibility%20of%20monitoring%20data%20and%20interpreting%20its%20meaning%20could%20make%20things%20worse%2C%20increasing%20hypervigilance%20and%20potentially%20worsening%20anxiety%20or%20postpartum%20OCD%2C%26quot%3B%20Sogand%20Ghassemi%2C%20a%20perinatal%20psychiatrist%20who%20practices%20in%20Brooklyn%20Park%2C%20Minnesota%2C%20says.%20In%20an%20ideal%20world%2C%20new%20parents%20would%20become%20more%20confident%20in%20reading%20and%20responding%20to%20their%20baby's%20cues%20without%20feeling%20the%20need%20to%20rely%20on%20gadgets%20and%20apps.%20And%20it's%20not%20only%20the%20parents%20whose%20emotional%20well-being%20stands%20to%20benefit%20from%20a%20more%20intuitive%20dynamic%20of%20communication%20and%20care.%20%26quot%3BOver%20time%2C%20this%20supports%20the%20baby's%20ability%20to%20develop%20self-soothing%20skills%2C%20which%20is%20important%20for%20resilience%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghassemi%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20raising%20her%20own%20two%20children%2C%20Guarnotta%2C%20the%20Long%20Island%20psychologist%2C%20was%20firmly%20%26quot%3Banti-baby%20monitor%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20It's%20a%20matter%20of%20personal%20preference%2C%20she%20tells%20me.%20Seeing%20other%20parents%20obsess%20over%20surveilling%20their%20babies%20was%20enough%20to%20convince%20her%20she%20was%20better%20off%20going%20the%20old-fashioned%20route%3A%20listening%20for%20cries%20and%20responding%20to%20them.%20A%20fancy%2C%20camera-equipped%20monitor%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20her%20anything%20she%20couldn't%20hear%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20already%20an%20anxious%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20Guarnotta%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20really%20want%20any%20part%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fkelli-maria-korducki%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EKelli%20Mar%C3%ADa%20Korducki%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20journalist%20whose%20work%20focuses%20on%20work%2C%20tech%2C%20and%20culture.%20She's%20based%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-parents-baby-gear-children-tech-ai-data-tracking-apps-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741767481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cf12a1585f1dff88b1a835%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-parents-baby-gear-children-tech-ai-data-tracking-apps-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20AI%20strollers%20to%20%26quot%3Bsmart%20socks%2C%26quot%3B%20gadgets%20for%20newborns%20are%20getting%20weird.%20Millennial%20parents%20can't%20get%20enough.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelli%20Mar%C3%ADa%20Korducki)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-parents-baby-gear-children-tech-ai-data-tracking-apps-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTamil%20Nadu%2040%20Years%20Ahead%20Of%20North%20States%26quot%3B%3A%20MDMK%20MP%20On%20Language%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20language%20row%20in%20Parliament%2C%20a%20Tamil%20Nadu%20MP%20has%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bnorthern%20states%20are%2040%20years%20behind%26quot%3B%20the%20southern%20state%2C%20and%20that%20people%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20dominate%20almost%20all%20spheres%20because%20of%20a%20two-language%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDurai%20Vaiko%2C%20MP%20from%20Marumalarchi%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(MDMK)%20and%20son%20of%20party%20chief%20Vaiko%2C%20recounted%20a%20meeting%20with%20Union%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan.%20Mr%20Vaiko%20had%20accompanied%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Education%20Minister%20Anbil%20Mahesh%20Poyyamozhi%2C%20who%20urged%20the%20Union%20Minister%20to%20release%20funds%20under%20the%20PM%20Schools%20for%20Rising%20India%20(PM%20SHRI)%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Education%20Minister%20then%20said%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20to%20sign%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%2C%20which%20lays%20down%20a%20three-language%20policy.%20%26quot%3BOur%20education%20minister%20said%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20excelled%20in%20PM%20SHRI%20scheme%2C%20so%20we%20are%20supposed%20to%20get%20funds.%20Why%20are%20you%20tying%20it%20up%20with%20NEP.%20He%20(Pradhan)%20said%2C%20'Tamil%20Nadu%20is%2040%20years%20behind%20and%20you%20people%20should%20wake%20up%2C%20why%20are%20u%20not%20letting%20students%20learn%20Hindi%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaiko%20said%20when%20he%20got%20the%20opportunity%20to%20speak%2C%20he%20told%20the%20minister%2C%20%26quot%3BTamil%20Nadu%20is%20not%2040%20years%20behind.%20Compared%20to%20northern%20states%2C%20we%20are%2040%20years%20ahead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MDMK%20leader%20said%20political%20parties%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20except%20the%20BJP%2C%20have%20been%20stressing%20that%20they%20won't%20accept%20a%20three-language%20policy.%20%26quot%3BSince%20the%20NEP%20insists%20on%20a%20three-language%20formula%2C%20we%20have%20suggested%20certain%20changes.%20If%20they%20bring%20in%20the%20changes%2C%20we%20don't%20mind%20signing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaiko%2C%20who%20represents%20Tiruchirapalli%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20stressed%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20parties%20are%20not%20against%20Hindi.%20%26quot%3BHindi%20Pracharak%20Sabha%20has%20been%20functioning%20in%20Chennai%20for%2060-70%20years.%20but%20we%20don't%20want%20imposition%20of%20Hindi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20batted%20for%20English%20and%20said%20it%20was%20a%20means%20of%20communicating%20with%20the%20people%20and%20India%20needs%20to%20master%20it%20as%20it%20pushes%20to%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20people%20of%20South%20(India)%2C%20English%20has%20been%20a%20means%20of%20progress.%20Tamilians%20dominate%20worldwide%2C%20across%20sectors%2C%20be%20it%20IT%20or%20medical%20science.%20They%20are%20dominating%20because%20of%20English%20proficiency%20and%20how%20did%20we%20get%20there%3A%20because%20of%20a%20two-language%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20parties%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20the%20Centre%20are%20locked%20in%20a%20face-off%20over%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20and%20the%20three-language%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Education%20Minister%20Pradhan%20has%20accused%20the%20MK%20Stalin%20government%20of%20creating%20%26quot%3Bfear%20psychosis%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20three-language%20formula%20while%20doing%20little%20to%20promote%20Tamil%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20that%20while%20students%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20are%20increasingly%20opting%20for%20English%2C%20the%20DMK%20government%20is%20questioning%20the%20need%20for%20a%20three-language%20formula.%20%26quot%3BNobody%20is%20imposing%20anything%20on%20anyone.%20This%20is%20a%20democratic%20society%20and%20the%20order%20of%20the%20time%20is%20you%20have%20to%20be%20multilingual%2C%26quot%3B%20Pradhan%20said.%20%26quot%3BOpposition%20to%20NEP%202020%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20preservation%20of%20Tamil%20pride%2C%20language%20and%20culture%20but%20everything%20to%20do%20with%20gaining%20political%20dividends.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741767480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fj5egnd3g_vaiko-mp_625x300_12_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdurai-vaiko-tamil-nadu-language-row-national-education-policy-tamil-nadu-40-years-ahead-of-north-states-mdmk-mp-on-language-row-7906611%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20language%20row%20in%20Parliament%2C%20a%20Tamil%20Nadu%20MP%20has%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bnorthern%20states%20are%2040%20years%20behind%26quot%3B%20the%20southern%20state%2C%20and%20that%20people%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20dominate%20almost%20all%20spheres%20because%20of%20a%20two-language%20formula.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdurai-vaiko-tamil-nadu-language-row-national-education-policy-tamil-nadu-40-years-ahead-of-north-states-mdmk-mp-on-language-row-7906611%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20economic%20growth%20to%20exceed%206.5%25%20in%20FY26%2C%20says%20Moody's%20Ratings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741767260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-s-economic-growth-to-exceed-6-5-in-fy26-says-moody-s-ratings-125031200486_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Moody's%20said%20that%20following%20a%20temporary%20slowdown%20in%20mid-2024%2C%20India's%20economic%20growth%20is%20expected%20to%20reaccelerate%20and%20record%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20rates%20among%20large%20economies%20globally%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-s-economic-growth-to-exceed-6-5-in-fy26-says-moody-s-ratings-125031200486_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Government%20not%20privatising%20telecom%20firms%20BSNL%2C%20MTNL%2C%20says%20minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741767009000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Findia-bsnl-mtnl-privatisation-telecom-public-sector-4g-network-125031200507_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20February%2C%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20reportedly%20approved%20Rs%206%2C000%20crore%20(Rs%2060%20billion)%20towards%204G%20network%20expansion%20of%20MTNL%20and%20BSNL%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Findia-bsnl-mtnl-privatisation-telecom-public-sector-4g-network-125031200507_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Can%20Congress%20Ever%20Return%20In%20Gujarat%3F%20It%20Needs%20To%20Do%20These%203%20Things%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20recently%20threw%20an%20open%20challenge%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20Congress%20would%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202027%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20he%20highlighted%20several%20challenges%20the%20party%20faces%20in%20accomplishing%20his%20%E2%80%98Mission%20Gujarat'.%20The%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20alleged%20that%20a%20section%20of%20partymen%20in%20the%20state%20has%20been%20in%20%26quot%3Bcollusion%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20that%20only%20after%20getting%20rid%20of%20such%20leaders%20the%20Congress%20will%20be%20able%20to%20do%20well%20in%20the%20state%2C%20where%20it%20has%20been%20out%20of%20power%20for%2030%20years%20now.%20Speaking%20to%20Congress%20workers%20in%20Gujarat%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Rahul%20said%20that%20the%20revival%20of%20the%20party%20in%20the%20state%20was%20not%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctwo-to-three-year%E2%80%9D%20but%20a%20%E2%80%9C50-year%20project%E2%80%9D%20adding%20that%20even%20if%20the%20party%20had%20to%20remove%20%E2%80%9C20-30%20people%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20would%20do%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul's%20comments%20have%20sparked%20controversy.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20alleging%20his%20party%2C%20people%2C%20constitutional%20institutions%2C%20and%20media%2C%20he%20has%20started%20blaming%20his%20own%20people.%20I'll%20suggest%20he%20do%20self-introspection%20instead%20of%20blaming%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20BJP%20leader%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%2C%20highlighting%20the%20Congress's%20internal%20struggles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%202022%20Experience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20the%20rhetoric%2C%20defeating%20the%20BJP%20in%20Gujarat%20is%20no%20easy%20task.%20The%20Congress%20was%20routed%20here%20in%202022%2C%20winning%20just%2017%20seats%20(60%20less%20than%20in%202017)%20with%20a%2027%25%20vote%20share%20(a%20drop%20of%2015%20percentage%20points).%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20which%20was%20just%20making%20its%20electoral%20debut%20in%20the%20state%2C%20ended%20up%20bagging%20an%20impressive%2013%25%20votes%E2%80%94at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20Congress.%20This%20also%20resulted%20in%20a%20record%20mandate%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20got%20156%20seats%20with%20a%2053%25%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202022%20results%20were%20a%20big%20setback%20for%20the%20Congress%20considering%20its%20performance%20in%202017%2C%20when%20it%20had%20won%2077%20seats%20and%20scored%20a%2042%25%20vote%20share%2C%20pushing%20the%20BJP%20to%20less%20than%20a%20hundred%20seats%3B%20the%20latter%20got%20just%20seven%20more%20seats%20than%20a%20simple%20majority.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20things%20the%20Congress%20must%20focus%20on%20to%20change%20its%20fate%20in%20Gujarat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EHigh%20Command%20Needs%20To%20Introspect%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%2C%20to%20be%20fair%2C%20Rahul%20is%20not%20wrong%20in%20his%20analysis%20about%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20the%20state%20jeopardising%20the%20party's%20prospects.%20Each%20assembly%20term%2C%20it%20sees%20a%20clutch%20of%20MLAs%20switching%20to%20the%20BJP.%20The%20usual%20trajectory%20is%20that%20they%20resign%2C%20become%20BJP%20candidates%20in%20by-polls%2C%20and%20return%20to%20the%20assembly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%202017%20and%202022%2C%20some%20three%20dozen%20Congress%20MLAs%20and%20leaders%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20Even%20in%20the%20current%20assembly%2C%20the%20party's%20tally%20is%20down%20to%2013.%20Four%20MLAs%20resigned%2C%20joined%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20then%20won%20the%20by-polls%20held%20recently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%20cannot%20escape%20full%20responsibility%20for%20the%20party's%20sorry%20state.%20Even%20after%20its%20stellar%20performance%20in%20the%202017%20elections%2C%20when%20it%20had%20benefited%20from%20the%20Patidar%20agitation%2C%20it%20ended%20up%20losing%20young%20firebrand%20leaders%20like%20Hardik%20Patel%20and%20Alpesh%20Thakor%20to%20the%20BJP.%20While%20Patel%20alleged%20that%20there%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20seriousness%20about%20all%20issues%20in%20the%20Congress's%20senior%20leadership%2C%20Thakor%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bweak%20leaders%26quot%3B%20were%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20affairs%20and%20that%20the%20OBC%20community%20wasn't%20getting%20the%20representation%20it%20deserved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20consistently%20enjoyed%20a%20strong%20vote%20share%20of%2038%25%20to%2042%25%20between%20the%202002%20and%202017%20elections.%20However%2C%20internal%20sabotage%20and%20its%20inability%20to%20present%20an%20alternative%20vision%20gave%20way%20to%20the%20opposition%20AAP%20to%20claim%20some%20space%20in%20the%20state.%20According%20to%20exit%20polls%20after%20the%202022%20polls%2C%2013%25%20of%20Leuva%20Patels%2C%206%25%20of%20Kadva%20Patels%2C%206%25%20of%20OBCs%2C%2020%25%20of%20SCs%2C%205%25%20of%20STs%20and%2041%25%20of%20Muslims%20deserted%20the%20party%2C%20in%20comparison%20to%202017.%20Had%20AAP%20not%20been%20in%20the%20fray%2C%20the%20Congress%20theoretically%20might%20have%20won%2055%20seats%20in%20the%20last%20assembly%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFind%20Serious%20Leaders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHerein%20lies%20the%20second%20correction.%20Today%2C%20the%20Congress%20needs%2C%20more%20than%20anything%20else%2C%20to%20identify%20leaders%20who%20stand%20with%20the%20public%2C%20fight%20for%20them%20and%20respect%20them%2C%20and%20have%20the%20Congress%20in%20their%20heart.%20Those%20who%20do%20not%20fall%20into%20this%20category%20need%20to%20be%20weeded%20out.%20The%20control%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20in%20the%20words%20of%20Rahul%2C%20%C2%A0should%20also%20be%20with%20such%20leaders.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20moment%20we%20do%20this%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Gujarat%20will%20want%20to%20storm%20into%20the%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20make%20this%20possible%2C%20the%20old%20guard%20will%20need%20to%20make%20space%20for%20new%20leaders%20who%20can%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20raising%20local%20issues.%20The%20AAP's%20losses%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20dent%20in%20Kejriwal's%20clean%20image%20are%20opportunities%20that%20the%20Congress%20must%20bank%20on%20in%20order%20to%20regain%20the%20vote%20it%20had%20lost%20to%20the%20party%20in%20Gujarat.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWoo%20The%20Urban%20Voters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20has%20a%20strong%20base%20in%20Gujarat's%20rural%20areas%20(109%20seats)%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20the%20upper%20hand%20in%20urban%20seats%20(74).%20But%2C%20with%20Gujarat's%20high%20urban%20population%2C%20the%20Congress%20cannot%20really%20afford%20to%20go%20down%20without%20a%20fight%20in%20such%20constituencies.%20In%202017%2C%20it%20was%20leading%2062-43%20in%20rural%20areas%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20while%20in%20urban%20areas%2C%20it%20trailed%20at%2015-57.%20Of%20the%2036%20purely%20urban%20seats%20in%20three%20big%20cities%E2%80%94Ahmedabad%2C%20Vadodara%2C%20Gandhinagar%E2%80%94the%20Congress%20could%20win%20just%20five.%20To%20improve%20its%20tally%20in%20these%20areas%20in%202027%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20have%20to%20win%20over%20the%20dominant%20middle%20class%20here%2C%20which%20favours%20a%20%E2%80%98business-friendly'%20BJP%20over%20an%20apparently%20%E2%80%98pro-Muslim'%20Congress.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20these%20three%20steps%2C%20it%20would%20be%20difficult%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20even%20dream%20of%20making%20a%20comeback%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20BJP's%20strongest%20fortress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741767000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-10%2Frahul-gandhi-ahmed-patel-gujarat-afp_650x400_61508665139.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcan-congress-ever-return-in-gujarat-it-needs-to-do-these-3-things-7906531%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20brass%20can't%20escape%20full%20responsibility%20for%20the%20party's%20sorry%20state.%20Even%20after%20its%20stellar%20performance%20in%20the%202017%20elections%2C%20it%20ended%20up%20losing%20young%20firebrand%20leaders%20like%20Hardik%20Patel%20and%20Alpesh%20Thakor%20to%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcan-congress-ever-return-in-gujarat-it-needs-to-do-these-3-things-7906531%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Miami%20millennial%20explains%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20travel%20to%20rural%20Alaska%20to%20help%20locals%20file%20taxes%2C%20saving%20some%20thousands%20in%20fees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221922%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karen%20Lapekas%20takes%20a%20photo%20in%20front%20of%20a%20plane%20in%20Alaska%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d061aab8b41a9673fa48a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221442%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKaren%20Lapekas%2C%20a%20Florida-based%20tax%20attorney%2C%20flew%20thousands%20of%20miles%20to%20help%20remote%20Alaskans%20file%20their%20taxes.%3Cp%3EKaren%20Lapekas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20millennial%20tax%20attorney%20braved%20Alaska's%20cold%20for%20the%20Volunteer%20Income%20Tax%20Assistance%20Project.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20VITA%20program%20helps%20low-income%2C%20disabled%2C%20and%20limited%20English-speaking%20Alaskans%20with%20tax%20filing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKaren%20Lapekas%20faced%20frozen%20pipes%20and%20frostbite%20risks%20while%20assisting%20remote%20communities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFiling%20and%20preparing%20taxes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%2Fhow-to-file-taxes%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNo%2520matter%2520how%2520many%2520times%2CApril%252015%2520tax%2520filing%2520deadline.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecan%20be%20stressful%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%20imagine%20doing%20it%20in%20-25-degree%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaren%20Lapekas%2C%20a%20tax%20attorney%20from%20Miami%2C%20did%20just%20that.%20From%20the%20end%20of%20February%20through%20early%20March%2C%20she%20traveled%20to%20three%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-to-live-work-utqiagvik-alaska-polar-night-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremote%20towns%20in%20Alaska%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Alaska%20Volunteer%20Income%20Tax%20Assistance%20Project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaunched%20this%20year%2C%20the%20program%20is%20a%20collaboration%20between%20the%20Alaska%20Business%20Development%20Center%20and%20the%20American%20Bar%20Association.%20It%20offers%20free%20tax%20help%20to%20residents%20who%20earn%20%2454%2C000%20or%20less%2C%20persons%20with%20disabilities%2C%20and%20limited%20English-speaking%20taxpayers%20who%20need%20assistance%20preparing%20their%20taxes.%20The%20two%20organizations%20have%20worked%20in%20previous%20years%20to%20help%20other%20taxpayers%20in%20the%20state%20prepare%20and%20file%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELapekas%20spent%2011%20days%20helping%20to%20file%20around%2085%20tax%20returns.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20wasn't%20locating%20a%20stray%20W-2%2C%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-long-does-it-take-to-get-frostbite-or-hypothermia-2014-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20in%20subzero%20temperatures%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20farther%20we%20got%20north%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoldest-temperature-on-record-every-state%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20more%20extreme%20the%20conditions%20got%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lapekas.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20one%20building%20we%20worked%20at%20that%20didn't%20have%20working%20bathrooms%20because%20the%20pipes%20had%20frozen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222938%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20building%20in%20Point%20Hope%20Alaska%20is%20covered%20in%20snow.%20The%20sign%20reads%20Inupiat%20Community%20of%20the%20Arctic%20Slope.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d0639cb8b41a9673fa4923%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222203%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELapekas's%20temporary%20office%20when%20working%20in%20Point%20Lay%2C%20Alaska.%3Cp%3EKaren%20Lapekas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a4c41de4-038e-4544-9531-264c372b6d93%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESubzero%20temperatures%20presented%20challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELapekas%2C%2042%2C%20was%20formerly%20a%20senior%20attorney%20with%20the%20IRS%20Office%20of%20Chief%20Counsel%20before%20she%20left%20to%20start%20her%20own%20private%20tax%20litigation%20business.%20She's%20been%20representing%20clients%20against%20the%20IRS%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20landing%20in%20Anchorage%2C%20Lapekas%20and%20her%20team%20of%20three%20underwent%20a%20final%20day%20of%20in-person%20training%20before%20they%20were%20flown%20out%20to%20villages%20in%20northern%20regions%20of%20the%20state.%20They%20volunteered%20in%20Kotzebue%2C%20Point%20Hope%2C%20and%20Point%20Lay%20%E2%80%94%20the%20last%20village%20had%20less%20than%20300%20people%20and%20temperatures%20reached%20-56%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Weather%20Channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20any%20bit%20of%20skin%20showing%20after%20just%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20you%20can%20get%20frostbite%2C%26quot%3B%20Lapekas%20said.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20villagers%20did%20get%20frostbite%20walking%20to%20the%20center%20where%20we%20were%20preparing%20tax%20returns%2C%20and%20they%20lived%20maybe%20three%20blocks%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELapekas%20said%20she%20and%20her%20colleagues%20slept%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20a%20community%20center%20and%20schools%20in%20villages%20without%20hotels.%20They%20ate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-keep-food-from-spoiling-in-a-power-outage-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edehydrated%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20store%20and%20fresh%20food%20was%20scarce%2C%20Lapekas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karen%20Lapekas%20takes%20a%20picture%20with%20dried%20food%20of%20black%20beans%20and%20rice%20she%20had%20for%20dinner.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d05fa269253ccddf98e1f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKaren%20Lapekas%20relied%20on%20dehydrated%20foods%20while%20in%20Alaska.%3Cp%3EKaren%20Lapekas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be18f0d6-4e01-42a2-b578-ff1fdd61ff4a%5C%22%3ERemote%20villagers%20faced%20hurdles%20filing%20returns%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20members%20of%20these%20communities%2C%20the%20VITA%20program%20was%20an%20opportunity%20to%20get%20assistance%20filing%20their%20taxes%20electronically%2C%20Lapekas%20said.%20She%20added%20that%20villagers%20have%20had%20trouble%20filing%20their%20taxes%20by%20mail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20were%20in%20Point%20Hope%2C%20for%20example%2C%20we%20found%20out%20that%20their%20post%20office%20was%20essentially%20closed%2C%26quot%3B%20Lapekas%20said%20of%20the%20village%20that's%20home%20to%20850%20people.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20Alaska%20VITA%20program%2C%20Lapekas%20said%20villagers%20had%20to%20fly%20to%20Anchorage%20and%20pay%20accountants%20to%20prepare%20their%20taxes.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20costs%20for%20villagers%20between%20flights%2C%20hotels%2C%20and%20accounting%20fees%20could%20reach%20%242%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20Lapekas%20was%20told%20by%20Alaskans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20exorbitant%20amount%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20simplicity%20of%20their%20return%20and%20their%20modest%20income%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELapekas%20and%20her%20colleagues%20worked%20long%20shifts%20during%20their%2011-day%20stay.%20She%20said%20on%20one%20day%20they%20started%20at%209%20a.m.%20and%20prepared%20returns%20until%20after%20midnight%20without%20taking%20a%20break.%20Many%20of%20Lapekas'%20clients%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-work-teacher-tiny-village-alaskan-bush-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworked%20in%20schools%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20support%20services%20for%20their%20communities%2C%20while%20others%20were%20part%20of%20subsistence%20communities%20that%20relied%20on%20whaling%2C%20hunting%2C%20and%20other%20natural%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karen%20Lapekas%20takes%20a%20selfie%20in%20front%20of%20two%20bowhead%20whale%20jaws%20that%20form%20an%20arch.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d06148585f1dff88b1c64d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKaren%20Lapekas%20visited%20the%20Utqiagvik%20Whale%20Bone%20Arch%2C%20a%20popular%20tourist%20attraction%20in%20Barrow%2C%20Alaska.%3Cp%3EKaren%20Lapekas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20entirely%20indigenous%20cultures%2C%26quot%3B%20Lapekas%20said.%20Indigenous%20Alaskans%20make%20up%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cityofkotzebue.gov%2Fabout-us%23%3A~%3Atext%3DKotzebue%2520has%2520a%2520population%2520of%2Cin%2520the%2520North%2520Slope%2520Borough.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E70%25%20of%20Kotzebue's%20population%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.north-slope.org%2Four-communities%2Fpoint-lay%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E88%25%20of%20Point%20Lay's%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.north-slope.org%2Four-communities%2Fpoint-hope%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DI%25C3%25B1upiat%2520make%2520up%2520eighty%252Dnine%2Csubsistence%2520hunting%252C%2520fishing%2520and%2520whaling.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E89%25%20of%20Point%20Hope's%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20made%20filing%20taxes%20for%20Alaskans%20in%20native%20communities%20unique%2C%20was%20that%20most%20individuals%2C%20including%20children%2C%20had%20income%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20many%20clients%20received%20money%20through%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falaska-permanent-fund-basic-income%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlaska%20Permanent%20Fund%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fancsaregional.com%2Feconomic-impacts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Alaska%20Native%20Regional%20Corporation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222358037d-40b1-4f76-bbea-d68bcb8f50be%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20rewards%20of%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Lapekas's%20first%20time%20volunteering%20for%20this%20particular%20pro-bono%20initiative%2C%20and%20she%20hopes%20that%20she%20can%20return%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20something%20about%20pro%20bono%20work%20and%20volunteering%20that%20just%20revived%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Lapekas%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20gives%20my%20work%20purpose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Lapekas%20returned%20home%20to%20sunny%20Miami%2C%20she%20said%20she%20was%20most%20excited%20to%20see%20her%20two%20children%2C%20who%20are%20two%20and%20five%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20reminded%20myself%20that%20I%20want%20to%20be%20an%20example%20to%20my%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20Lapekas%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20them%20to