ader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxi-used-wall-of-soldiers-block-eye-contact-zuckerberg-book-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EXi%20Jinping%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20APEC%20summit%20in%20Lima%2C%20Peru.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20engineer%20a%20chance%20meeting%2C%20Wynn-Williams%20wrote%20that%20she%20arranged%20for%20Zuckerberg's%20keynote%20speech%20to%20take%20place%20before%20Xi's.%20She%20also%20secured%20a%20dressing%20room%20for%20Zuckerberg%20next%20to%20Xi's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20things%20didn't%20go%20according%20to%20plan.%20Zuckerberg%20ended%20up%20getting%20blocked%20from%20Xi's%20view%20by%20the%20Chinese%20leader's%20security%20detail%2C%20Wynn-Williams%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20phalanx%20of%20men%2C%20in%20identical%20gray%20uniforms%2C%20marching%20in%20formation%20past%20us.%20Mark%20stares%20in%20disbelief%2C%20mouth%20open.%20They%20just%20keep%20coming%2C%20dozens%20and%20dozens%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXi's%20men%20formed%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20Chinese%20wall%26quot%3B%20between%20Xi%20and%20Zuckerberg's%20dressing%20rooms%2C%20Wynn-Williams%20wrote.%20The%20men%20only%20dispersed%20after%20Xi%20entered%20his%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUh%2C%20I%20guess%20that%20pull-aside%20isn't%20going%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20told%20his%20staff%2C%20per%20Wynn-Williams'%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20approached%20for%20comment%20about%20Wynn-Williams'%20book%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Meta%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bfired%20for%20poor%20performance%20and%20toxic%20behavior%26quot%3B%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20book%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20out-of-date%20and%20previously%20reported%20claims%20about%20the%20company%20and%20false%20accusations%20about%20our%20executives%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Zuckerberg%20at%20Meta%20did%20not%20respond%2