%2C%20or%20has%20already%20won%2C%20the%20mayoral%20seat%20for%20nine%20of%2010%20civic%20bodies%2C%20including%20in%20Gurugram%20and%20Rohtak%2C%20the%20bastion%20of%20Bhupinder%20Hooda%2C%20one%20of%20the%20Congress'%20senior-most%20state%20leaders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20independent%20candidate%20-%20Dr%20Inderjit%20Yadav%2C%20a%20rebel%20BJP%20leader%20-%20is%20ahead%20in%20the%20tenth%2C%20Manesar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fairness%2C%20the%20Congress%20-%20which%20slumped%20to%20defeat%20in%20the%20Assembly%20election%20last%20year%20despite%20racing%20into%20a%20big%20early%20lead%20-%20has%20only%20fought%20local%20polls%20under%20its%20own%20symbol%20only%20once%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20though%2C%20the%20party%20fielded%20several%20candidates%2C%20including%20for%20the%20post%20of%20Mayor%20of%20Gurugram%2C%20which%20settled%20into%20a%20first%20direct%20contest%20-%20with%20the%20BJP%20-%20for%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20BJP%20unleased%20top%20leaders%20from%20the%20state%20-%20including%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Nayab%20Saini%20and%20his%20newly-elected%20Delhi%20counterpart%2C%20Rekha%20Gupta%20-%20during%20campaigning%2C%20which%20included%20door-to-door%20visits%20and%20grand%20roadshows.%20The%20Congress%20responded%20with%20former%20Rajasthan%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Sachin%20Pilot%20and%20Mr%20Hooda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20result%2C%20nevertheless%2C%20has%20been%20one-sided%2C%20with%20the%20incumbent%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Raj%20Rani%20leading%20the%20Congress'%20Seema%20Pahuja%20by%20over%2095%2C000%20votes%20after%20six%20rounds%20of%20counting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20Defeated%20In%20Rohtak%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20battle%20for%20Rohtak's%20mayoral%20seat%20was%2C%20on%20paper%2C%20a%20five-way%20contest%20between%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%2C%20and%20an%20indep