to%20signature%20burgers%20take%20years%20to%20reach%20customers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20plans%20to%20shake%20up%20operations%20and%20introduce%20new%20executive%20roles%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20takes%20years%20to%20introduce%20new%20burgers%2C%20its%20CEO%20says%2C%20and%20he%20wants%20to%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain's%20chief%20executive%2C%20Chris%20Kempczinski%2C%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20process%20of%20introducing%20new%20burgers%20and%20improving%20existing%20signature%20burgers.%20He%20made%20these%20comments%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fhospitality%2Fmcdonalds-revamps-ranks-to-speed-burger-breakthroughs-5786631e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20published%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKempczinski%20says%20he's%20switching%20things%20up%20in%20leadership%20and%20operations%20to%20make%20the%20company%20move%20faster.%20Part%20of%20that%20involves%20changing%20the%20job%20scopes%20of%20his%20leadership%20team%20to%20roll%20out%20new%20technology%20and%20products%20to%20its%20restaurants%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJill%20McDonald%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20company's%20international%20division%2C%20has%20been%20tapped%20to%20be%20the%20chain's%20first%20chief%20restaurant%20experience%20officer%20starting%20May%201.%20McDonald%20is%20a%20retail%20veteran%2C%20having%20held%20top%20roles%20at%20Marks%20and%20Spencer%20and%20Costa%20Coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe'll%20lead%20the%20team%20responsible%20for%20the%20company's%20innovation%2C%20supply%20chains%2C%20and%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20one%20person%20who's%20actually%20looking%20at%20all%20these%20tech%20things%20through%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20restaurant%20general%20manager%2C%26quot%3B%20Kempczinski%20said%20to%20the%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20not%20elaborate%20on%20how%20else%20he%20would%20speed%20up%20the%20burger%20development%20process.%20Representatives%20for%20McDonald's%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20query%20from%20Business%20Insider%20on%20the%20topic%2C%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Kempczinski%20also%20hinted%20at%20a%20more%20extensive%20drinks%20menu.%20He%20said%20he%20would%20get%20executives%20to%20focus%20exclusively%20on%20beverage%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20this%20would%20help%20the%20company%20find%20a%20way%20to%20keep%20customers%20in%20store%20and%20buying%20their%20drinks%20rather%20than%20going%20to%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20just%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20our%20menu%20offering%20doesn't%20give%20somebody%20a%20reason%20why%20they%20come%20to%20us%20for%20their%20food%20and%20they%20maybe%20go%20to%20the%20place%20next%20door%20to%20go%20get%20the%20beverage%2C%26quot%3B%20Kempczinski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKempczinski's%20comments%20come%20as%20the%20chain%20posted%20stagnant%20financial%20results%20in%202024.%20The%20chain's%20global%20comparable%20sales%20declined%200.1%25%20in%202024.%20It%20reported%20a%20full-year%20revenue%20of%20%2425.92%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20markets%20closed%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20McDonald's%20stock%20traded%20at%20%24306.8.%20It%20has%20risen%20about%204%25%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fast%20food%20industry%20is%20facing%20a%20wave%20of%20cost-conscious%20consumers%20in%20the%20US%C2%A0who%20are%20put%20off%20by%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-is-expensive-people-annoyed-eating-out-restaurant-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erising%20fast%20food%20product%20prices.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Some%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-low-income-diners-eat-at-home-prices-soar-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eopting%20to%20eat%20at%20home%3C%