0said%20that%20customers%20who%20don't%20qualify%20will%20pay%20for%20their%20first%20and%20second%20checked%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20Southwest's%20CEO%20Bob%20Jordan%20said%20that%20after%20fare%20and%20schedule%2C%20checked%20bags%20were%20the%20%26quot%3Bnumber%20one%20issue%20in%20terms%20of%20why%20customers%20choose%20Southwest%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20reiterated%20the%20stance%20on%20checked%20baggage%20again%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Tuesday's%20JPMorgan%20conference%2C%20he%20said%20the%20change%20would%20spur%20Southwest%20credit%20card%20enrollments%20and%20add%20revenue.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20carry%20nearly%20two%20times%20the%20bags%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20competition%2C%20which%20is%20costly%20on%20many%20fronts%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20is%20part%20of%20Southwest's%20larger%20business%20overhaul%20as%20the%20company%20faces%20investor%20pressure%20after%20a%20series%20of%20lackluster%20earnings.%20Passenger%20volumes%20are%20below%20pre-pandemic%20levels%20despite%20strong%20travel%20demand.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESouthwest's%20stock%20is%20down%2026%25%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20while%20United%20is%20up%20over%2080%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felliott-management-latest-fundraise-and-favorite-opportunities-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EElliott%20Investment%20Management%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20built%20up%20an%2011%25%20stake%20in%20the%20company%2C%20said%20the%20airline's%20decades-old%20strategies%20weren't%20working.%20The%20activist%20investor%20called%20for%20an%20overhaul%20of%20management%20and%20the%20board%20of%20directors.%20In%20October%2C%20Southwest%20added%20six%20directors%20from%20outside%20the%20company%20as%20part%20of%20a%20deal%20with%20Elliot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESouthwest%20abandoned%20i