Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20takeoff%2C%20the%20Cessna%20180%20aircraft%20crashed%20on%20the%20campus%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Agricultural%20Sciences%2C%20near%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20lowdown%20on%20what%20happened%20on%20April%2017%2C%202004%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20aircraft%2C%20a%20Cessna%20180%2C%20took%20off%20from%20the%20Jakkur%20airstrip%20at%2011.05%20am.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESoundarya%2C%20pregnant%20at%20that%20time%2C%20was%20travelling%20with%20her%20brother%2C%20Amarnath%2C%20BJP%20party%20worker%20Ramesh%20Kadam%2C%20and%20pilot%20Joy%20Philips%20to%20Karimnagar%2C%20then%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20was%20on%20her%20way%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20for%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20aircraft%20turned%20west%20before%20crashing%20on%20the%20campus%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Agricultural%20Sciences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20had%20reached%20a%20height%20of%20150%20feet%20(46%20m)%2C%20and%2C%20before%20achieving%20the%20required%20rate%20of%20climb%20speed%2C%20took%20a%20steep%20left%20turn%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20stall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20caught%20fire%20a%20few%20minutes%20into%20takeoff%20and%20crashed%20into%20the%20ground%20nose%20down.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBN%20Ganapathi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20two%20persons%20working%20on%20the%20experimental%20fields%20of%20the%20university%2C%20who%20rushed%20to%20the%20aircraft%20to%20save%20the%20passengers%2C%20said%20the%20plane%20wobbled%20before%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESM%20Krishna%2C%20the%20then%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20and%20Arun%20Jaitley%2C%20the%20Union%20Commerce%20Minister%20and%20then%20BJP%20state-in-charge%2C%20rushed%20to%20Jakkur%20after%20the%20crash.%20The%20BJP%20city%20unit%20also%20called%