0a%20train%20siege%20in%20southwestern%20Pakistan%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20they%20walked%20for%20hours%20through%20mountainous%20terrain%20to%20reach%20safety%2C%20forced%20to%20leave%20behind%20relatives%20from%20whom%20they%20were%20separated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERebels%20waging%20a%20war%20of%20independence%20against%20the%20Pakistani%20state%20set%20off%20explosions%20on%20the%20railway%20track%20in%20a%20remote%20area%20of%20Balochistan%2C%20forcing%20the%20train%20to%20a%20halt%20and%20taking%20more%20than%20450%20passengers%20hostage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20find%20the%20words%20to%20describe%20how%20we%20managed%20to%20escape.%20It%20was%20terrifying%2C%26quot%3B%20Muhammad%20Bilal%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilal%20had%20been%20traveling%20with%20his%20mother%20on%20the%20Jafar%20Express%20train%20when%20it%20was%20caught%20in%20the%20explosive%20crossfire%2C%20leaving%20at%20least%20three%20dead%2C%20according%20to%20a%20railway%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20100%20hostages%20have%20been%20freed%20from%20the%20train%2C%20which%20remains%20held%20up%20by%20rebel%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20heard%20an%20explosion%20followed%20by%20gunfire%20as%20rebels%20boarded%20the%20train%2C%26quot%3B%20passenger%20Allahditta%20told%20AFP%20at%20the%20train%20station%20in%20Mach%2C%20where%20the%20waiting%20area%20has%20been%20transformed%20into%20a%20makeshift%20hospital%20to%20treat%20the%20wounded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20began%20hiding%20under%20the%20seats%20in%20panic.%20They%20separated%20the%20men%20from%20the%20women.%20They%20allowed%20me%20and%20my%20family%20to%20go%20because%20I%20told%20them%20I'm%20a%20heart%20patient%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2049-year-old%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EID%20checks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20walked%20for%20a%20long%20time%20through%20the%20mountains%20to%20reach%20the%20nearest%20station.%20I%20haven't%20eaten%20since%20