C%20Rs%202%20Crore%20At%20Home%3A%20What%20Led%20To%20Ranya%20Rao's%20Arrest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20that%20Kannada%20actor%20Ranya%20Rao's%20gold%20smuggling%20attempt%20came%20to%20light%2C%20she%20was%20a%20passing%20through%20the%20green%20channel%2C%20an%20airport%20zone%20for%20those%20who%20have%20no%20items%20to%20declare%20to%20the%20customs%20department%2C%20with%2014%20kilograms%20of%20gold%20concealed%20on%20her%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20arriving%20at%20the%20Kempegowda%20International%20Airport's%20Terminal%202%20aboard%20an%20Emirates%20flight%20from%20Dubai%20on%20March%204%2C%20she%20was%20intercepted%20by%20Department%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%20officials%20based%20on%20specific%20intelligence.%20To%20questions%20on%20whether%20she%20had%20dutiable%20goods%2C%20gold%2C%20any%20other%20contraband%20to%20declare%20before%20the%20Indian%20Customs%2C%20Rao%20replied%20in%20the%20negative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rao%20did%20not%20make%20a%20baggage%20declaration%20with%20the%20Indian%20Customs%2C%20she%20also%20did%20not%20have%20a%20purchase%20receipt%20or%20documents%20to%20prove%20she%20legally%20bought%20the%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20metal%20detector%20door%20indicated%20presence%20of%20a%20metal%2C%20after%20which%20her%20hand%20baggage%20and%20trolley%20were%20scanned.%20However%2C%20nothing%20was%20found.%20Then%20Rao's%20personal%20examination%20revealed%20where%20the%20gold%20was.%20Gold%20bars%20were%20fastened%20to%20her%20waist%20and%20calf%20muscles%20using%20crepe%20bandage%20and%20tissues%2C%20while%20some%20bars%20and%20cut%20pieces%20were%20hidden%20in%20her%20shoes%20and%20pants'%20pockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20retrieval%20of%2014213.050%20grams%20of%2024%20karat%20gold%20from%20Rao%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20similar%20such%20seizures.%20The%20permitted%20threshold%20of%20carrying%20gold%20as%20per%20Customs%20Act%2C%201962%20is%20of%20the%20value%20of%20Rs%201%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20follow-up%20search%20at%20her%20Lavelle%20Road%20residence%20for%20goods%20liable%20to%20confiscation%20and%20documents%20relevant%20to%20investigation%20resulted%20in%20Rs%202.67%20crore%20cash%20and%20jewellery%20worth%20over%20Rs%202%20crore%20being%20found.%20She%20was%20unable%20to%20provide%20the%20source%20of%20the%20cash%20and%20invoices%20for%20the%20jewellery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Dubai%20Customs%20declarations%20from%20November%20and%20December%20last%20year%20showed%20that%20she%20had%20purchased%20gold%20from%20Dubai%20and%20had%20informed%20the%20Customs%20there%20that%20she%20intended%20to%20travel%20with%20it%20to%20Geneva.%20However%2C%20her%20travel%20history%20shows%20she%20deviated%20and%20landed%20in%20India%20with%20it.%20She%20was%20also%20charged%20with%20duty%20evasion%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%204.83%20crore%2C%20much%20higher%20than%20the%20Rs%2050%20lakhs%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20multiple%20visits%20to%20Dubai%20gave%20the%20authorities%20grounds%20to%20believe%20that%20she%20might%20continue%20smuggling%20gold%20into%20India%2C%20necessitating%20her%20arrest.%20Further%20factors%20behind%20her%20arrest%20were%20to%20prevent%20her%20from%20committing%20further%20such%20offences%20%26quot%3Bas%20she%20appears%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20syndicate%20with%20considerable%20resources%20and%20a%20sophisticated%20network%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20DRI%20arrest%20memo%2C%20she%20has%20not%20rendered%20full%20cooperation%20in%20the%20investigation%2C%20failing%20to%20disclose%20all%20facts.%20Rao's%20arrest%20will%20also%20prevent%20any%20attempts%20to%20tamper%20evidence%2C%20the%20memo%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrest%20memo%20also%20clarified%20that%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20arrest%2C%20she%20already%20had%20injury%20marks%20under%20her%20eyes%20sustained%20in%20a%20previous%20incident.%20This%20assumes%20significance%20as%20many%20news%20reports%20cla