0CT%20Ceremony%20Row%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20is%20unlikely%20to%20receive%20any%20%26quot%3Bformal%20clarification%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20ICC%20on%20the%20perceived%20snub%20during%20the%20closing%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20Dubai.%20India%20beat%20New%20Zealand%20by%20four%20wickets%20in%20the%20title%20clash%20on%20Sunday%20to%20win%20the%20tournament%20for%20the%20third%20time.%20The%20controversy%20erupted%20when%20Sumair%20Ahmed%2C%20who%20is%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20the%20PCB%20and%20was%20the%20tournament%20director%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20was%20not%20invited%20on%20stage%20for%20the%20final%20presentation.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20filed%20a%20formal%20complaint%20with%20the%20ICC%20as%20what%20happened%20is%20unacceptable%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20PCB%20official%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%20according%20to%20ICC%20sources%2C%20the%20PCB%20won't%20be%20given%20any%20formal%20explanation.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20PCB%20mandarins%20look%20up%2C%20even%20ICC%20CEO%20Geoff%20Allardice%20wasn't%20present%20on%20stage.%20The%20reason%20is%20protocol%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20ICC%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSumair%20Ahmed%20is%20an%20employee%20of%20the%20PCB%20and%20not%20an%20office-bearer.%20Also%20please%20check%20when%20has%20a%20tournament%20director%20been%20on%20stage%20for%20presentation%3F%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20give%20an%20example.%20ICC's%20new%20head%20of%20operations%20and%20communications%20Gaurav%20Saxena%20was%20once%20Tournament%20Director%20for%20Asia%20Cup%20in%20Dubai.%20Was%20he%20on%20stage%20for%20final%20presentation%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20ICC%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBCCI%20president%20Roger%20Binny%20presented%20the%20white%20jackets%20to%20India%20players%20and%20the%20medals%20to%20match%20officials%2C%20while%20ICC%20chairman%20Jay%20Shah%20handed%20the%20trophy%20to%20skipper%20Roh