%20a%20glossy%2C%20apricot-yellow%20mango%20with%20consistent%20yields.%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EImage%20credits%3A%20Amazon%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20new%20varieties%20reflect%20India%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20commitment%20to%20agricultural%20innovation%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20beloved%20mango%20continues%20to%20thrive%20in%20diverse%20conditions%20while%20meeting%20evolving%20market%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741602600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D412175%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you%20love%20mangoes%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20in%20for%20a%20treat!%20Farmers%20and%20scientists%20have%20been%20quietly%20working%20to%20bring%20us%20new%2C%20delicious%20varieties%E2%80%94sweeter%2C%20hardier%2C%20and%20full%20of%20surprises.%20From%20Arunika%20to%20Awadh%20Samridhi%2C%20these%20mangoes%20are%20changing%20the%20way%20we%20enjoy%20summer.%20Have%20you%20heard%20of%20them%20yet%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Megha%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jodhpur%20MBA%E2%80%99s%20Millet%20Creations%20Turn%20Into%20a%20Multi-Crore%20Bakery%2C%20Winning%20PM%E2%80%99s%20Praise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20years%20back%2C%20Jodhpur-based%20Amit%20Soni%20was%20tasked%20by%20the%20PUSA%20Institute%2C%20short%20for%20Indian%20Agricultural%20Research%20Institute%20(IARI)%20%E2%80%94%20to%20create%20millet-based%20confectioneries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20decided%20to%20craft%20a%20chocolate%20truffle%20cake%20using%20%3Cem%3Ebajra