s%20for%20students%20is%20conducted%20in%20two%20ways.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20method%20is%20through%20the%20programme%E2%80%99s%20website%2C%20which%20goes%20live%20in%20July%202025.%20This%20timing%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20results%20of%20various%20exams%2C%20which%20are%20typically%20declared%20in%20May%20and%20June.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20students%20who%20do%20not%20have%20access%20to%20a%20computer%20or%20any%20device%2C%20Cybage%20has%20set%20up%20a%20support%20system.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20student%20who%20does%20not%20have%20access%20to%20a%20computer%20or%20any%20device%20can%20come%20to%20Cybage%20at%20our%20office.%20We%20set%20up%20a%20kiosk%20at%20the%20entrance%20for%20these%20students%2C%20and%20one%20of%20our%20CSR%20volunteers%20helps%20them%20fill%20out%20the%20form%20and%20submit%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20method%20is%20through%20direct%20collaborations%20with%20colleges.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20direct%20tie-ups%20with%20colleges%2C%20where%20we%20inform%20them%20about%20CybageKhushboo.%20Every%20year%2C%20they%20receive%20applications%20and%20send%20us%20the%20ones%20they%20feel%20fit%20the%20criteria%20for%20the%20scholarships%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ritu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20CybageKhushboo%20has%20formed%20partnerships%20with%2019%20colleges%2C%20and%20the%20team%20continues%20to%20add%20more%20institutions%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Ritu%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9CEducation%20is%20not%20just%20about%20textbooks.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20building%20character%2C%20confidence%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20world.%20Through%20CybageKhushboo%2C%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20achieve%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Leila%20Badyari%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%20Cybage%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741349454000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2